			</icon>
			<text
			size="16.0"
			fontFamily="System"
			fontStyle="Regular"
			text="Creating opportunities to connect takes time, but can be the most valuable part of a workshop. When people from different backgrounds get to know each other it paves the way for resolving differences. While you build relationships, think about activities that support sharing of diverse perspectives and two-way engagement.">
